               <interp inst="t17560915-10" type="year" value="1756"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17560915-10" type="uri" value="sessionsPapers/17560915"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17560915-10" type="date" value="17560915"></interp>
               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17560915-10-off57-c70" targOrder="Y" targets="t17560915-10-defend88 t17560915-10-off57 t17560915-10-verdict60"></join>
         
               <p>331. (L.) 
               
                  <persName id="t17560915-10-defend88" type="defendantName">
                     Michael 
                     Hart 
                  <interp inst="t17560915-10-defend88" type="surname" value="Hart"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17560915-10-defend88" type="given" value="Michael"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17560915-10-defend88" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t17560915-10-off57" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17560915-10-off57" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17560915-10-off57" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing one silk handkerchief, value 2 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17560915-10-victim90" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Day 
                        <interp inst="t17560915-10-victim90" type="surname" value="Day"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17560915-10-victim90" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17560915-10-victim90" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17560915-10-off57 t17560915-10-victim90"></join>
                     </persName>
                      
                  , privately from his person
            </rs>, <rs id="t17560915-10-cd58" type="crimeDate">June the 10th</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17560915-10-off57 t17560915-10-cd58"></join>.* </p> 
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="175609150005"></xptr>Thomas Day. On the 10th of last June I was at <placeName id="t17560915-10-crimeloc59">Billingsgate</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17560915-10-crimeloc59" type="placeName" value="Billingsgate"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17560915-10-crimeloc59" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17560915-10-off57 t17560915-10-crimeloc59"></join>, about twelve o'clock. I had taken my handkerchief out of my breast pocket to wipe my fingers, having handled some mackerel, and put it into my coat pocket. In a minute's time 
               <persName id="t17560915-10-person91">
                  Thomas 
                  Yates 
               <interp inst="t17560915-10-person91" type="surname" value="Yates"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17560915-10-person91" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17560915-10-person91" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             said to me, Have you not lost your handkerchief? I felt, and said I had. He told me he'd shew me the person that had it, and took me to Darkhouse-lane, where he pointed to the prisoner. I went and charged him with it, but he denied it. I then went to take him into an alehouse, and observing his hand in his pocket I pull'd it out. He had my handkerchief in his hand, and I took it just as he was going to drop it (produced in court, and deposed to.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17560915-10-person92">
                  Thomas 
                  Yates 
               <interp inst="t17560915-10-person92" type="surname" value="Yates"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17560915-10-person92" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17560915-10-person92" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             confirm'd the account given by the prosecutor.</p>
               <p>The prisoner had nothing to say in his defence.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17560915-10-verdict60" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17560915-10-verdict60" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17560915-10-verdict60" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder1s"></interp>
               Guilty 10 d.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17560915-10-punish61" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17560915-10-punish61" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17560915-10-defend88 t17560915-10-punish61"></join>
               
                     <note>[Transportation. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
